p: Territory of Washington vs. Gus Beudjus &as}

Comes now the Grand Jury and by their foreman into presence of the said Grand Jury present to the Court one indictment against Gus. Beudjus, Robert Straugbeurd, Ben Frederickson, Peter Peterson, Frank Nelson, Fred Stromburger, John Bleuding, Andrew Johnson, Leander Brown, John Saxon, John Thompson, Alex Agreu, Thomas Jacobs, E. Emil, Andrew Anderson and Charles Burke for the crime of Malicious Mischief which they saythey find above bill in which twelve of their number concur which indictment is recovered by the Court and by the clerk did filed in open court in the presence of said Grand Jury
